    <title>銀山溫泉｜銀白色的溫泉小鎮</title>
    <link href="http://bificoo.com/2016/03/25/%E9%8A%80%E5%B1%B1%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89%EF%BD%9C%E9%8A%80%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89%E5%B0%8F%E9%8E%AE/"/>
    <id>http://bificoo.com/2016/03/25/銀山溫泉｜銀白色的溫泉小鎮/</id>
    <published>2016-03-24T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-04-21T16:21:31.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>這次的旅行是一場意外，在同事熱心幫助下，我們來到東北自助旅行，考量這次搭乘的是紅眼班機，選擇銀山溫泉作為我們放鬆的第一站</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>凌晨的飛機在到達日本時，時間也才快 5 點，為了兌換 JR EAST PASS，我們在機場小休片刻，機場的大家都在椅子上肆無忌憚的舒服睡著，可是我無法，只能昏昏沈沈的半睡半醒</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1588/25353651332_38e271ec8e_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1588/25353651332_38e271ec8e.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1588/25353651332_38e271ec8e_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1588/25353651332_38e271ec8e_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/50 f/6.3 ISO400</div></div>
<p>等兌換好 PASS 後，看看時間也 8 點了，剛好是上班的尖峰時刻，這種感覺很奇特，因為大家都穿著西裝、制服，準備去上班、上學，可是我們卻穿著便服準備出去玩，有一種蹺班出去玩的興奮感！</p>
<h3 id="駅弁屋祭"><a href="#駅弁屋祭" class="headerlink" title="駅弁屋祭"></a>駅弁屋祭</h3><div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1590/25176530040_47d19d75cd_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1590/25176530040_47d19d75cd.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1590/25176530040_47d19d75cd_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1590/25176530040_47d19d75cd_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/125 f/6.3 ISO800</div></div>
<p>在出發前，我們先到駅弁屋祭外帶鐵路便當，作為中餐備用，因為我們接下來的旅程只會離都市越來越遠，吃飯的選擇自然少，當然，順便體驗看看日本鐵路便當也是目的之一XD（雖然好貴..）</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1566/24841568674_0b2730d810_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1566/24841568674_0b2730d810.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1566/24841568674_0b2730d810_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1566/24841568674_0b2730d810_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/60 f/6.3 ISO400</div></div>
<p>這瓶水讓我看到日本人眼裡的產品細節，蓋子上有特別加工，打開後瓶蓋不會亂掉一通</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1632/25379253981_b0047814ed_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1632/25379253981_b0047814ed.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1632/25379253981_b0047814ed_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1632/25379253981_b0047814ed_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/80 f/6.3 ISO400</div></div>
<p>駅弁屋祭據說集結了 170 種全日本各地的特色鐵路便當，每一種便當的外觀都包裝得相當精緻，精緻到我們不清楚裡面的味道好不好，不過黑面倒是很快就決定了，從一進門開始眼神就死盯著米澤牛鰻魚雙拼便當</p>
<p>所以，他在車上開動了（其實剛吃完早餐，然後這個是要當中餐的計劃就..）</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1498/25379253521_0d3c846bb2_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1498/25379253521_0d3c846bb2.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1498/25379253521_0d3c846bb2_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1498/25379253521_0d3c846bb2_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/320 f/6.3 ISO100</div></div>
<p>雖然一開始睡眠不足精神不好，但是很快的我們的旅程就是一直坐著，所以也不會太累，倒是窗外的風景讓人擔心起來，究竟東北會不會下雪呢？，懷著這樣的想法，我無法安心睡覺，所以又是一段昏昏沈沈的休息時光</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25445991756_31a2bd4d74_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25445991756_31a2bd4d74.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25445991756_31a2bd4d74_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25445991756_31a2bd4d74_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/640 f/6.3 ISO100</div></div>
<p>然後，我的擔心是多餘的，當我看到這個畫面，藍天白雪天氣超好，我可以安心睡覺了（？）</p>
<h3 id="大石田駅"><a href="#大石田駅" class="headerlink" title="大石田駅"></a>大石田駅</h3><div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1637/25379275261_eecf4cf42c_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1637/25379275261_eecf4cf42c.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1637/25379275261_eecf4cf42c_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1637/25379275261_eecf4cf42c_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/1250 f/6.3 ISO400</div></div>
<p>大石田駅我來了～咦？怎麼只剩下陰天白雪？我內心開始充滿疑惑，不過，有下雪還是很開心啦！</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1708/24845431913_a26689f8e2_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1708/24845431913_a26689f8e2.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1708/24845431913_a26689f8e2_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1708/24845431913_a26689f8e2_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/50 f/6.3 ISO1600</div></div>
<p>大石田是小車站，但是小的很可愛很溫馨，在這溫馨的小車站裡，我們吃著剛才買的鐵路便當，配著味噌飲料（？）</p>
<p>這是一位路過的和藹媽媽，跟我們交談時送的，雖然我其實聽不懂他在說什麼，但我最後有記得說「ありがとうございます」</p>
<blockquote>
<p>注意：東北地區的通車時間長，搭乘的班次也較少，一定要實際去計算每一班車的搭乘時間，才不會耽誤行程！</p>
</blockquote>
<p>在一開始規劃行程時，我們試圖在第一天去山寺晃晃再回到銀山溫泉，後來實際計算交通時程時，才發現這樣的行程會很趕，難得跑這麼遠來，還是多留點時間好好的享受旅程吧！</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1529/25353717342_52d5699e5f_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1529/25353717342_52d5699e5f.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1529/25353717342_52d5699e5f_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1529/25353717342_52d5699e5f_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/800 f/6.3 ISO100</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/25472171725_d4d3b08c7d_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/25472171725_d4d3b08c7d.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/25472171725_d4d3b08c7d_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/25472171725_d4d3b08c7d_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/400 f/8.0 ISO100</div></div>
<p>在大石田邊填飽肚子，邊等待瀧見舘的接駁車，接下來又是一段坐著的旅程，除了中間有讓我們下來看看超肥大的鵝</p>
<h3 id="瀧見舘"><a href="#瀧見舘" class="headerlink" title="瀧見舘"></a>瀧見舘</h3><div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1661/24845445093_9d36fe7a5e_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1661/24845445093_9d36fe7a5e.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1661/24845445093_9d36fe7a5e_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1661/24845445093_9d36fe7a5e_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/30 f/8.0 ISO1600</div></div>
<p>搭乘下午 1:40 的接駁車，所以我們早早就來到銀山溫泉，接駁車先送我們回瀧見舘放行李，記錄一下整齊的房間，一泊二食是我們這趟旅程住最貴的一天</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1559/25446037856_5fecee09eb_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1559/25446037856_5fecee09eb.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1559/25446037856_5fecee09eb_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1559/25446037856_5fecee09eb_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/250 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25104628929_15c7c56872_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25104628929_15c7c56872.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25104628929_15c7c56872_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1569/25104628929_15c7c56872_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/800 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1615/25379331731_15c8212844_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1615/25379331731_15c8212844.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1615/25379331731_15c8212844_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1615/25379331731_15c8212844_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/800 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<p>瀧見舘是唯一遠離溫泉小街的旅館，要小走一段路才會到達溫泉街</p>
<h3 id="銀山溫泉"><a href="#銀山溫泉" class="headerlink" title="銀山溫泉"></a>銀山溫泉</h3><div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1490/25104695739_86319ecb8c_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1490/25104695739_86319ecb8c.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1490/25104695739_86319ecb8c_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1490/25104695739_86319ecb8c_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/250 f/8.0 ISO800</div></div>
<p>這一條短短的溫泉街，大概十幾分鐘就可以逛完了，但是這裏的建築物、風景真的很美，放慢速度在這裡待很久也不會膩</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1570/24841660864_575acdeee2_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1570/24841660864_575acdeee2.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1570/24841660864_575acdeee2_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1570/24841660864_575acdeee2_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/100 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1675/25379385881_7a4fba182d_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1675/25379385881_7a4fba182d.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1675/25379385881_7a4fba182d_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1675/25379385881_7a4fba182d_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/125 f/8.0 ISO800</div></div>
<p>連接兩邊的橋中，只有一座是紅色的，就在能登屋旅館的前頭，謠傳是阿信拍攝的現場之一，看起來就很氣派</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1576/25176657400_fd6e8b939a_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1576/25176657400_fd6e8b939a.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1576/25176657400_fd6e8b939a_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1576/25176657400_fd6e8b939a_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/250 f/8.0 ISO100</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1488/25104680319_087acfb9c2_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1488/25104680319_087acfb9c2.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1488/25104680319_087acfb9c2_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1488/25104680319_087acfb9c2_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/30 f/8.0 ISO100</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1612/25176664050_caff15f36b_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1612/25176664050_caff15f36b.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1612/25176664050_caff15f36b_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1612/25176664050_caff15f36b_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/60 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1652/25472250515_24664f2cb9_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1652/25472250515_24664f2cb9.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1652/25472250515_24664f2cb9_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1652/25472250515_24664f2cb9_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/25 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1703/25446098776_4f1f859e31_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1703/25446098776_4f1f859e31.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1703/25446098776_4f1f859e31_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1703/25446098776_4f1f859e31_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/200 f/8.0 ISO400</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1644/24845525923_78328db344_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1644/24845525923_78328db344.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1644/24845525923_78328db344_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1644/24845525923_78328db344_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/125 f/8.0 ISO800</div></div>
<p>回旅館後先泡溫泉，因為白天和晚上男湯女湯會交換，現在去泡，晚上再泡一次，就可以看到兩邊的風景</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1550/25379420671_ffd427497d_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1550/25379420671_ffd427497d.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1550/25379420671_ffd427497d_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1550/25379420671_ffd427497d_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/60 f/3.2 ISO800</div></div>
<p>泡完溫泉後的睡意超濃，加上一整天的舟車勞頓，我們立刻陷入昏迷狀態，直到有人敲門要送晚餐進來，才從睡夢中驚醒，趕快擦擦口水，請服務生進來</p>
<p>一整頓晚餐下來超飽，印象最深刻的就是這個牛肉，米澤牛一片、山形牛一片，總共兩片，吃完想把整頓晚餐都換成他們</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1583/25104749279_55c2041818_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1583/25104749279_55c2041818.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1583/25104749279_55c2041818_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1583/25104749279_55c2041818_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/30 f/2.8 ISO1600</div></div>
<p>吃飽喝足後，搭上瀧見舘的接駁車再去一趟溫泉街，夜晚和白天的溫泉街大不相同，兩側的旅館點上燈後，增添了點神秘的感覺，真的有神隱少女故事中的情境</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1451/24845583623_d3d71e4c4b_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1451/24845583623_d3d71e4c4b.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1451/24845583623_d3d71e4c4b_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1451/24845583623_d3d71e4c4b_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/50 f/2.8 ISO3200</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1560/25446158486_75d82ac5ee_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1560/25446158486_75d82ac5ee.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1560/25446158486_75d82ac5ee_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1560/25446158486_75d82ac5ee_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/15 f/2.8 ISO3200</div></div>
<p>夜晚的溫度又更冷冽了，幸好旅館都會提供超保暖大衣和雨鞋，有種想外帶一件回家的感覺</p>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1646/24845592263_36875c34b2_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1646/24845592263_36875c34b2.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1646/24845592263_36875c34b2_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1646/24845592263_36875c34b2_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/25 f/2.8 ISO1600</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1602/25176744170_181e30fbfd_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1602/25176744170_181e30fbfd.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1602/25176744170_181e30fbfd_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1602/25176744170_181e30fbfd_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/50 f/2.8 ISO1600</div></div>
<div class="img-outter"><div class="img-wrapper"><img data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1685/25353874922_27fe67cd1a_n.jpg 320w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1685/25353874922_27fe67cd1a.jpg 500w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1685/25353874922_27fe67cd1a_c.jpg 800w,https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1685/25353874922_27fe67cd1a_b.jpg 1024w" width="1024" class="lazyload"></div><div class="img-exif">1/50 f/2.8 ISO1600</div></div>
<p>從好冷的溫泉街回到瀧見舘，再泡一次溫泉剛剛好，把今天的疲累丟掉，明天才有精神冒險下去！</p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;這次的旅行是一場意外，在同事熱心幫助下，我們來到東北自助旅行，考量這次搭乘的是紅眼班機，選擇銀山溫泉作為我們放鬆的第一站&lt;/p&gt;
    
